    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Do you ever feel like you're being watched?</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/54651b3e37693d8b149e527129134aca.poster.avif?t=1746035270\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/54651b3e37693d8b149e527129134aca.webm?t=1746035270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/54651b3e37693d8b149e527129134aca.mp4?t=1746035270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GANGSTALK</strong> is a psychological horror game from the POV of your stalkers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cam, an urban explorer, is past their breaking point. They've been under relentless surveillance by the megacorp <strong>PANDO</strong>. Desperate for answers, they infiltrate a secret company town — <i>one that doesn’t exist on any map</i>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Do you ever feel like you're being watched?</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/41e9366fd76be52562963cfebf14a00d.poster.avif?t=1746035270\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/41e9366fd76be52562963cfebf14a00d.webm?t=1746035270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/41e9366fd76be52562963cfebf14a00d.mp4?t=1746035270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of Cam as they explore the tangled streets of <strong>Kudzu Vale</strong>, piecing together the conspiracy. Watch them through the fragmented perspectives of CCTV Cameras, Devices, Agents, and the enigmatic Datamoshers.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Kudzu Vale </i></strong><i> </i>— Explore the dreamlike town of Kudzu Vale and reveal its mysteries. Every clue you uncover will draw you deeper into the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Datamoshers</strong></i>  — Beware the distorted entities that stalk you. Escape or be consumed by their corruption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Every second counts</strong> </i>— Discover the truth before reality disintegrates around you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>You're being watched.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/18787c97aa1d5255cebe941b4ef1ab74.poster.avif?t=1746035270\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/18787c97aa1d5255cebe941b4ef1ab74.webm?t=1746035270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235140/extras/18787c97aa1d5255cebe941b4ef1ab74.mp4?t=1746035270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
